Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎来短暂和平的比斯科帝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和公主殿下本应过着平静的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但突然的宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一场赌上国家宝剑的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下和勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的战斗即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:01:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致蓓琪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:05.19,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\fs55\blur4\3c&H3B5D92&\fsp2\pos(281,710)}「开战之日」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久疏问候抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下有场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会取胜的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发送
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 今天是比斯科帝和加雷特的大战
